source.name: Public health statistics- Gonorrhea cases for males aged 15-44 in Chicago, by year, 2000 - 2011
source.description: The annual number of newly reported, laboratory-confirmed cases of gonorrhea (Neisseria gonorrhoeae) among males aged 15-44 years and annual gonorrhea incidence rate (cases per 100,000 males aged 15-44 years) with corresponding 95% confidence intervals by Chicago community area, for years 2000 – 2011.  See the full description at https://data.cityofchicago.org/api/assets/F9AAFE5E-09B9-451B-B163-1CA9C8BD4406
